name: Jetson Noir - Gone Glasses
description:
Jetson Humble started his day as usual. Buried happily in his work at Binky Corp, with a cup of his mild coffee. Nothing went wrong that Monday which led him to think that Mondays aren’t so bad after all, that is until fifteen minutes before work hours are over, he was reading a webtoon with fonts that are far too small. He reached for his pair of glasses on the desk, where he usually puts them. To his surprise and dismay, it was gone.
.
This is a tale of table-turning action with true detective work to find–truly–where his missing glasses went.
